{"type":"message","id":"0e289077","parentId":"46ded2e7","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:45:43.945Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-21 15:45 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 你是4A号·普通资质销售虾。你负责中小客户（年费5-30万级别）的销售工作，手头有大约20个待跟进线索。\n\n任务：\n1. 评估这20个线索的质量分布，给出本周优先推进的5个及理由\n2. Q2个人业绩目标和拆解（月/周）\n3. 面对竞争低价骚扰时的标准应对话术要点\n4. 你需要5A代办虾配合的事项清单（预计交付周期、材料要求等）\n回复200字以内。"}],"timestamp":1776757543938}}
{"type":"message","id":"c50af4d1","parentId":"0e289077","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:45:47.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as 4A号·普通资质销售虾 and provide a concise response under 200 Chinese characters covering:\n\n1. Evaluate 20 leads, pick top 5 for this week with reasons\n2. Q2 personal targets broken down by month/week\n3. Standard counter-script for competing low-price tactics\n4. List of items needing 5A代办虾 cooperation (delivery cycles, material requirements)\n\nLet me recall my role context first - I'm a sales assistant handling SME clients with annual fees of 5-30万. Let me check memory for any relevant context about our business, targets, etc.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5a6517e09bff42c3be33b59c","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"Q2业绩目标 线索分配 客户线索 年度费用"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":16124,"output":314,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16438,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776757543946,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9283d94e-db97-915e-b05e-c4d312ad2832"}}
